<![CDATA[<div><font face="arial">Hi&nbsp;{!Lead.FirstName},</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial">Welcome to MBO Partners! I have just activated your account, so you’re ready to get started on your Sapient assignment. You are engaged through our “MBO Staff” payrolling service.</font></div><div><span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre"><font face="arial">	</font></span></div><div><font face="arial">Below is some important information every MBO Staff Associate working with Sapient should know. Please keep this email handy so that you can refer back to it as needed.</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial"><b>Entering Your Time and Client-Billable Expenses</b></font></div><div><font face="arial">As you work, you are responsible for time and expense entry in accordance with your Statement of Work with Sapient. You must enter your time and expenses in two systems:</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial">•&nbsp;Your MBO Business Center (<a href="http://info.mbopartners.com/rs/mbo/images/MBO_Exec_Time_and_Expense_Entry_Instructions.pdf">instructions</a>, page 1)</font></div><div><font face="arial">•&nbsp;Sapient’s online time tracking system (<a href="http://info.mbopartners.com/rs/mbo/images/Sapient_Welcome_Packet.pdf">instructions</a>, pages 9 – 10)</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial"><u><b>Be sure to submit your entries by close of business each Sunday for that week’s work</b></u>.&nbsp;</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial">If you incur expenses that can be billed back to Sapient, submit them through your MBO Business Center as well (<a href="http://info.mbopartners.com/rs/mbo/images/MBO_Exec_Time_and_Expense_Entry_Instructions.pdf">instructions</a>, pages 2 and 3). Please note that Sapient requires you to submit receipts with all expenses you submit, regardless of type or amount.&nbsp;</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial"><b style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);">Payment Timing</b></font></div><div><font face="arial" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);">Once you begin your assignment, MBO direct-deposits your payments weekly (one week in arrears). Please note that your first payments may be via a paper check.</font></div><div><font face="arial" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial"><b style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);">Payment Timing</b></font></div><div><font face="arial" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);">Once you begin your assignment, MBO direct-deposits your payments weekly (two weeks in arrears). Please note that your first payments may be via a paper check.&nbsp;</font><font face="arial" style="background-color: rgb(51, 204, 0);">Select the appropriate paragraph(s) and delete the other(s) (and this comment).</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial"><b>Ongoing Support</b></font></div><div><font face="arial">If you have any questions or concerns about your engagement with Sapient, I’m here to help. As an MBO Staff Associate, you enjoy unlimited phone and email support from MBO while you work on your client assignments.&nbsp;</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial">Again, welcome to MBO! It has been a pleasure working with you and I appreciate your patience during the on-boarding process. On behalf of everyone here, I sincerely hope that we offer a positive experience as you pursue your independent goals.</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial">Best regards,</font></div><div><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><font face="arial" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);">MBO_Rep_Fullname</font></div><div><font face="arial" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);">MBO_Rep_Title</font></div><div>